<paragraph blockId="78.[151,1436,761,822]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,304,761,786]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">Distribution.</emphasis>
Widespread in the Indo-West Pacific; extending south to central Zululand (Leadsman Shoal); local material 
<quantity box="[250,350,797,822]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.25" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" unit="m" value="52.5" valueMax="100.0" valueMin="5.0">5–100 m</quantity>
, but mostly &lt;
<quantity box="[504,561,798,822]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" unit="m" value="20.0">20 m</quantity>
(no data for living specimens).
</paragraph>
